{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "傳曰：「有從輕而重，公子之妻為其皇姑。有從重而輕，為妻之父母。有從無服而有服，公子之妻為公子之外兄弟。有從有服而無服，公子為其妻之父母。」", "text_normalized": "傳曰：「有從輕而重，公子之妻為其皇姑。有從重而輕，為妻之父母。有從無服而有服，公子之妻為公子之外兄弟。有從有服而無服，公子為其妻之父母。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "傳曰：「母出，則為繼母之黨服；母死，則為其母之黨服。」為其母之黨服，則不為繼母之黨服。", "text_normalized": "傳曰：「母出，則為繼母之黨服；母死，則為其母之黨服。」為其母之黨服，則不為繼母之黨服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "三年之喪，既練矣，有期之喪，既葬矣，則帶其故葛帶，絰期之絰，服其功衰。有大功之喪，亦如之。小功，無變也。麻之有本者，變三年之葛。", "text_normalized": "三年之喪，既練矣，有期之喪，既葬矣，則帶其故葛帶，絰期之絰，服其功衰。有大功之喪，亦如之。小功，無變也。麻之有本者，變三年之葛。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "既練，遇麻斷本者，於免，絰之；既免，去絰。每可以絰必絰；既絰，則去之。", "text_normalized": "既練，遇麻斷本者，於免，絰之；既免，去絰。每可以絰必絰；既絰，則去之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "小功不易喪之練冠，如免，則絰其緦小功之絰，因其初葛帶。緦之麻，不變小功之葛；小功之麻，不變大功之葛。以有本為稅。", "text_normalized": "小功不易喪之練冠，如免，則絰其緦小功之絰，因其初葛帶。緦之麻，不變小功之葛；小功之麻，不變大功之葛。以有本為稅。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "殤：長、中，變三年之葛。終殤之月算，而反三年之葛。是非重麻，為其無卒哭之稅。下殤則否。", "text_normalized": "殤：長、中，變三年之葛。終殤之月算，而反三年之葛。是非重麻，為其無卒哭之稅。下殤則否。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "君為天子三年，夫人如外宗之為君也。世子不為天子服。", "text_normalized": "君為天子三年，夫人如外宗之為君也。世子不為天子服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "君所主：夫人、妻、大子適婦。", "text_normalized": "君所主：夫人、妻、大子適婦。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "大夫之適子為君、夫人、大子，如士服。", "text_normalized": "大夫之適子為君、夫人、大子，如士服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "君之母，非夫人，則群臣無服。唯近臣及仆驂乘從服，唯君所服，服也。", "text_normalized": "君之母，非夫人，則群臣無服。唯近臣及仆驂乘從服，唯君所服，服也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "公為卿大夫錫衰以居，出亦如之。當事則弁絰。大夫相為，亦然。為其妻，往則服之，出則否。", "text_normalized": "公為卿大夫錫衰以居，出亦如之。當事則弁絰。大夫相為，亦然。為其妻，往則服之，出則否。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the", "source_id": "liji-036-subjects-for-questions-about-the__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《服問》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "凡見人無免絰，雖朝於君，無免絰。唯公門有稅齊衰。傳曰：「君子不奪人之喪，亦不可奪喪也。」傳曰：「罪多而刑五，喪多而服五，上附下附列也。」", "text_normalized": "凡見人無免絰，雖朝於君，無免絰。唯公門有稅齊衰。傳曰：「君子不奪人之喪，亦不可奪喪也。」傳曰：「罪多而刑五，喪多而服五，上附下附列也。」", "notes": ""}
